thread.title: John Estrada
thread.title_full: Test Equipment Depot reviewed by John Estrada

author: John Estrada
title: John Estrada
text: Ordering was simple shipped as promised. But a signature was requested upon delivery. I have been waiting all day for 2 days now and as soon as I leave fed ex shows up and leaves a missed you note. When I try to schedule a time with fed ex or pick up from depot fed ex wants me to open an account and leave a credit card number for billing !!!! ALL I WANT IS MY PACKAGE
